General.Name: Errawarra Resources Ltd
General.Description: Errawarra Resources Ltd engages in the mineral exploration and project development in Australia. It explores for gold, nickel, scandium, cobalt, and copper deposits. The company holds 80% interests in Andover West project located in Western Australia. It also holds interests in Errabiddy project located in the Gascoyne Region of Western Australia; Binti Binti gold project, which covers an area of approximately 116 square kilometers located in Western Australia; and Fraser Range project that covers an area of approximately 105 square kilometers located in Western Australia. Errawarra Resources Ltd was incorporated in 2012 and is based in Perth, Australia.
